snippet.title: An Evening at the Library - Doki Doki Blue Skies Teaser #6 (Yuri's Route)
snippet.description:
Sorry it's been a while since we last uploaded! To compensate, please enjoy the first teaser for Yuri's route. 

Here, we see MC slowly coax Yuri out of her shell. What better way to do so than through literature?
